    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Nos <persName key="#Princeps #Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis" ref="#people/3019"
                            >Robbertus</persName>, divina ordinante clementia Capuanorum <rs
                            key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>, ad salutem et remedium animarum quondam
                            <rs key="#Princeps">principum</rs>
                        <persName key="#Princeps #grandparentOf" ref="#people/3001"
                            >Richardi</persName>, scilicet <rs key="#grandparentOf">avi</rs>, ac
                            <persName key="#Princeps #parentOf" ref="#people/3002"
                            >Iordani</persName>
                        <rs key="#parentOf">patris</rs>, et <persName key="#Princeps #siblingOf"
                            ref="#people/3010">secundi Richardi</persName>
                        <rs key="#siblingOf">fratris</rs> nostri, <rs key="#Intercessory"
                            >interventum</rs> quondam <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Witness #Other_palatine_officer" ref="#people/3035"
                            >Odoaldi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer">camerarii</rs> nostri et aliorum nostrorum
                        fidelium, per hoc principale scriptum, in perpetuum, concedimus et
                        confirmamus <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/3000">Sancti
                            Laurentii</orgName>, sito circa <rs key="#Walls">muros</rs> nostrae
                            <placeName key="#Cities #Walls" ref="#places/4000">Aversane</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Cities">urbis</rs>, et domini <persName
                            key="#Abbots #Personal_rank" ref="#people/3033">Matthei</persName>
                        <rs key="#Personal_rank">venerabili</rs>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbati</rs>, eiusque successoribus, videlicet <rs
                            key="#Value #Public_exactions">octingentos tarenos Amalfetanos</rs> de
                            <rs key="#Lakes">lacu</rs>
                        <placeName
                            key="#Lakes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Public_exactions #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            ref="#places/701">Patriense</placeName>, quos predictus Iordanus
                        princeps, pater meus, et secundus Richardus frater meus praefato monasterio
                        concesserunt, et potestatem et licentiam predictus dominus Mattheus abbas,
                        et omnes successores illius, et pars ipsius monasterii habeant dandi <rs
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">piscationes</rs> ipsius
                        aque Patriae, pro predictis octingentis tarenis illis <rs key="#Merchants"
                            >negotiatoribus</rs> nostrae Aversanae urbis, quibus dare voluerint,
                        absque omni contrarietate et molestia nostra nostrorumque successorum,
                        principum, comitum vel vice comitum, castaldeorum et omnium ordinatorium, et
                        omnium mortalium personae. Quod si quis huius nostrae congessionis et
                        confirmationis paginae contemptor extiterit, aut contra hoc principale
                        scriptum agere praesumpserit, <rs key="#Penalty">viginti libras auri
                            purissimi</rs> persolvat, medietatem praedicto monasterio et praefato
                        domino Mattheo venerabili abbati, eiusque successoribus, et medietatem
                        nostro palatio. Et soluta poena haec nostra concessio firma atque
                        inviolabilis maneat in perpetuum. Et ut hoc scriptum firmius credatur et
                        diligentius ab omnibus observetur, manu propria subscribens, corroboravimus,
                        et nostri sigilli impressione iussimus insigniri. Ex iussione prefatae
                        potestatis, scripsi ego <persName key="#Writer #Judge" ref="#people/3012"
                            >Quiriacus</persName>, <rs key="#Judge">palatinus iudex</rs>, in anno
                        Dominicae incarnationis millesimo centesimo sexto decimo, et nono anno
                        principatus praefati domini Roberti <rs key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis"
                            >gloriosi</rs> principis, mense martio, per indictionem nonam + Signum
                            <persName key="#Intercessory #Witness #Other_palatine_officer"
                            ref="#people/3035">Odoaldi </persName>camerarii. + Signum <persName
                            key="#Witness" ref="#people/3040">Hugonis de Nipolita</persName>. +
                        Signum <persName ref="#people/3032" key="#Witness">Amonis de
                            Argentia</persName>.</ab>
